test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (4 == 3)
 +  where 4 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x766c86b234c0>([-89])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x766c86b234c0> = [[1, -89], [1, -89, 1], [-89], [-89, 1], [1, -89], [1, -89, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 89 == -89
 +  where 89 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -89])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
